Here you need to add parentheses around addition and subtraction:

    let rec to_ten x =
      if x = 10 then x 
      else if x &lt; 10 then to_ten (x + 1)
      else to_ten (x - 1)

Otherwise, operator precedence makes `to_ten x + 1` read as `((to_ten x) + 1)`, which results in an infinite loop. See [7.7.1  Precedence and associativity](https://caml.inria.fr/pub/docs/manual-ocaml/expr.html#sec133)

